<%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8" pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
<title>예약 완료</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap-grid.css">
<style type="text/css">
* {
	box-sizing: border-box;
	padding: 0;
	margin: 0;
}
section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background-image: url('images/starback.jpg');
    background-repeat:no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
}
.pricing-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    list-style: none;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 12px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    padding: 30px 100px;
}
.pricing-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    margin: 7px;
    color: #666;
    font-size: 14px;
}
.pricing-header {
    padding: 0 0 50px;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: transparent;
}
.columns {
	margin: 0 auto;
	background: #00000085;
    text-align: center;
	/* min-width: 700px;
    max-width: 1000px; */
}
.columns .pricing-header .price {
    color: #f8b753 !important;
    background-color: transparent;
}
.pricing-header h2 {
    font-size: 1.8em;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 40px;
}
.pcInfo {
	margin-bottom: 30px;
	color: #666;
}
.currency,
.value {
	font-size: 3rem;
	font-weight: 300;
}
.value {
    font-size: 5em;
    font-weight: 300;
}
.currency {
    color: #f8b753;
}
.columns .currency {
	color: #666;
}
.currency {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    vertical-align: top;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
}
.pricing-body {
	color: #666;
}
.pricing-features:after {
	content: "";
	display: table;
	clear: both;
}
.pricing-features span {
	display: block;
	margin-bottom: 5px;
	font-weight: 600;
}
.pricing-features li {
    padding: 1em;
    font-size: 18px;
    text-align: left;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    color: white;
}
.pricing-features span {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 0;
}
.pricing-footer {
    display: flex;
	width: 100%;
    padding: 1.8em 0;
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 1;
    justify-content: center;
}
.pricing-footer::after {
    display: none;
}
.columns .button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1em 2em;
    color: #f8b753;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 20px;
    text-indent: 0;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    transition: all .6s;
}
.columns .button {
    background-color: #f8b753;
	color: #eee;
	/* flex: 1; */
	border: 0;
    width: 200px;
    margin: 0 10px;
}
.columns .button:hover {
	cursor: pointer;
	opacity: .8;
}
.cancel {
    background-color: #990000 !important;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
	<section>
		<div class="col-sm-8 col-md-8 col-lg-8 columns">
			<ul class="pricing-wrapper">
				<%-- <li class="pricing-label">No. ${resv.resv_num}</li> --%>
				<li>
					<div class="pricing-header">
						<div class="pcInfo">
							<h2>${resv.pc_name}</h2>
							<span>${resv.pc_addr}</span>
						</div>
						<div class="price">
							<span class="currency"></span>
							<span class="value">${resv.resv_price}</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="pricing-body">
						<ul class="pricing-features">
							<li>이용 세대 : <span>${resv.generation}</span></li>
							<li>이용 인원 : <span>${resv.maxLen}</span> 명</li>
							<li>이용 시간 : <span>${resv.resv_hours}</span> 시간</li>
							<li>이용 일시 : <span>${resv.resv_start}</span> ~ <span>${resv.resv_end}</span></li>
							<li>선택 좌석 : <span>${resv.seat_num}</span></li>
							<li>결제 방법 : <span>${resv.payment}</span></li>
						</ul>
						<%-- <input type ="hidden" name ="email" value="${loginUser.email}"> --%>
					</div>
					<div class="pricing-footer">
						<input class="button goMain" type="button" value="홈으로">
						<input class="button resvCancel" type="button" value="예약 취소"> 
						
					</div>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>
	
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function(){
	$('.pricing-footer .goMain').click(function(){
		location.href = 'main';
	});
	$('.pricing-footer .resvCancel').click(function(){
		location.href = 'pcResvDelete?resv_num=${resv_num}';
	});
});
</script>
</body>
</html>